{"tid":1923354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全球排中】 #NOTCHINA 行動","createTime":"2020-03-13T04:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T12:14:49.000Z","uid":282534,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ace12f527ff97b982adb2a3964890ce50cef074","tid":1923354,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 【全球排中】#NOTCHINA 行動 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於目前全球都被<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">中國肺炎</span></span></strong>搞到滿城風雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其以 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">意大利</span> , <span style=\"color: red;\">日本</span> , <span style=\"color: pink;\">韓國</span></span></strong> 為重災區<br />\n當中<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一帶一路</span></span></strong>國家都被中國害餐死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而病毒既源頭 正正就係中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地更加要食住呢個勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n插多中國幾刀 令中國損失擴大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連侵侵都開口轉發叫隻毒做<span style=\"color: red;\"> 中國肺炎</span>既時候 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你仲唔識做?</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1ez6PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1ez6PA.jpg&h=7172d33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且仲搞到NBA停賽之餘仲有球員中招<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wc7eAju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWc7eAju.jpg&h=b9f67eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【武漢肺炎】NBA 猶他爵士再多一人中招　<br />\n後衛 Donovan Mitchell 確診<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3aOvimf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aOvimf&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=2a404e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3aOvimf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲搞到 加拿大總理老婆都中埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgTNaTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgTNaTg.jpg&h=ecccc739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【武漢肺炎】加拿大總理杜魯多妻子確診<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3cWniBu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cWniBu&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=6538e902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3cWniBu</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但中國仲厚面皮到唔認<br />\n【武漢肺炎】中國卸責！外交部「戰狼」發言人質疑美軍帶病毒到武漢 <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200313&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60706845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200313%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60706845&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=561b6df6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200313%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60706845&h=97513dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200313&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60706845</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>依家全世界都屌緊中國</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要藉住今次既事件 , 同全球受<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>武漢肺炎</strong></span>害既國家<span style=\"color: gold;\"> WE CONNECT </span><br />\n當中經考慮後 使用 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#hashtag </span></strong><br />\n係最最最可以同全球咁多國家CONNECT埋一齊既方法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無成本既方法 WHY NOT ?</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是發起本次行動<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請由即時起 <span style=\"color: red;\">係你每日出PO既地方加上</span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#NOTCHINA</span></strong> 作為本次行動之重點<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">E.G : Facebook , IG , twitter , reddit </span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的在於推動全球排中<br />\n然後將全球焦點極力集中係中國同香港上<br />\n唔好睇少每一個人講一句說話既力量 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一句說話足以影響一個人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocNNHmY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocNNHmY.jpg&h=0b8aa6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhPDO2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhPDO2E.jpg&h=a3ec72d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2ArXV0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2ArXV0.jpg&h=e2966d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTMrdum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTMrdum.jpg&h=1e718619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#2 為大家提供更多延伸閱讀資料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ：排中咪姐係排自己，鬼佬分撚到咩？<br />\n<br />\nA：鬼佬分唔到咪教佢分囉，唔好限制自己嘅能力。更何況而家嘅情況有分別咩？<br />\n與其阻止佢哋排中，仲不如教佢哋點排排得更有效<br />\n<br />\nQ：NOTCHINA我不是中国(支那)??<br />\n<br />\nA：當初有諗過用Chinese定China好，但考慮到Chinese 關種族事，外國人會混亂，而China比較具體同印象深刻啲，所以都係決定用Chi - na<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【全球排中】倫敦響起「Fuck China!」號角聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1921761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1921761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"406ba35195e801195fcb3ec80707e5fc8321a354","tid":1923354,"uid":282534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n<br />\n第一單緊係被人打個位<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FcWguC56JkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.c